am\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 274}, {\"ngram\": \"Some fascinating insights\", \"from\": 275, \"to\": 300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tatjana Smith has been a household name around South Africa for a while.\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 382, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 357, \"end\": 369, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"score\": 0.9999999993447091, \"rank\": 6.445342555711539e-10, \"text\": \"South Africa\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Africa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tatjana Smith\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 323}, {\"ngram\": \"a household name\", \"from\": 333, \"to\": 349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, her antics at the Paris 2024 Olympics have taken things up a notch.\", \"from\": 383, \"to\": 459, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her antics\", \"from\": 392, \"to\": 402}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 415}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 429}, {\"ngram\": \"things\", \"from\": 441, \"to\": 447}, {\"ngram\": \"a notch\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 458}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Did you know she missed qualification for the 200m breaststroke at Rio 2016 by 0.01 seconds?\", \"from\": 460, \"to\": 552, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"qualification\", \"from\": 484, \"to\": 497}, {\"ngram\": \"the 200m breaststroke\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 523}, {\"ngram\": \"Rio\", \"from\": 527, \"to\": 530}, {\"ngram\": \"0.01 seconds\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Info viaolympics.com'sofficial website.\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 593, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Info viaolympics.com'sofficial website\", \"from\": 554, \"to\": 592}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A personal highlight for Tanja was winning 200m breaststroke gold at the 2018 Commonwealth Games on the Gold Coast of Australia.\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 723, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 620, \"end\": 625, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanja_von_Lahnstein\", \"score\": 0.9480720222188794, \"rank\": 0.05477218667390453, \"text\": \"Tanja\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanja_von_Lahnstein\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tanja_von_Lahnstein\"}, {\"begin\": 713, \"end\": 722, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.966565364822722, \"rank\": 0.03458873240317739, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A personal highlight\", \"from\": 595, \"to\": 615}, {\"ngram\": \"200m breaststroke gold\", \"from\": 638, \"to\": 660}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2018 Commonwealth Games\", \"from\": 664, \"to\": 691}, {\"ngram\": \"the Gold Coast\", \"from\": 695, \"to\": 709}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Having my parents in the stands with some of our family friends and winning my first major competition.\\\"\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my parents\", \"from\": 733, \"to\": 743}, {\"ngram\": \"the stands\", \"from\": 747, \"to\": 757}, {\"ngram\": \"our family friends\", \"from\": 771, \"to\": 789}, {\"ngram\": \"my first major competition\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 828}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My love for swimming makes me want to get up every morning and go to training.\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 911, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My love\", \"from\": 833, \"to\": 840}, {\"ngram\": \"swimming\", \"from\": 845, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"training\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 910}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's like my second home.\", \"from\": 912, \"to\": 937, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my second home\", \"from\": 922, \"to\": 936}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Being fortunate enough to travel the world doing what I love, seeing new places and meeting new people and sports heroes, motivates me a lot.\", \"from\": 938, \"to\": 1079, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 971, \"to\": 980}, {\"ngram\": \"new places\", \"from\": 1007, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"new people\", \"from\": 1030, \"to\": 1040}, {\"ngram\": \"sports heroes\", \"from\": 1045, \"to\": 1058}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The most important thing every young swimmer should realise is that nothing is impossible.\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1170, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The most important thing\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1104}, {\"ngram\": \"every young swimmer\", \"from\": 1105, \"to\": 1124}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1148, \"to\": 1155}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They only need to believe and be prepared to put in the long and hard hours.\\\"\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1248, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the long and hard hours\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When reflecting on missing out on the 200m breaststroke in Rio, Smith was typically philosophical and upbeat about one of the biggest setbacks in her professional career.\", \"from\": 1250, \"to\": 1420, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1309, \"end\": 1312, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999967729383799, \"rank\": 3.2270718741005723e-06, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 200m breaststroke\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1305}, {\"ngram\": \"Smith\", \"from\": 1314, \"to\": 1319}, {\"ngram\": \"the biggest setbacks\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1392}, {\"ngram\": \"her professional career\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"2016 was a bit of a disappointment, but I knew everything happens for a reason.\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 1432, \"to\": 1437}, {\"ngram\": \"a disappointment\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1457}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 1470, \"to\": 1480}, {\"ngram\": \"a reason\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1501}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wasn't ready at that time.\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1531, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that time\", \"from\": 1521, \"to\": 1530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We got our hopes up and then I kind of got a dip, creating all that expectation.\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1612, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our hopes\", \"from\": 1539, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"a dip\", \"from\": 1575, \"to\": 1580}, {\"ngram\": \"all that expectation\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1611}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My fall was quite big, and I had to try and fall in love with the sport again.\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1691, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My fall\", \"from\": 1613, \"to\": 1620}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 1665, \"to\": 1669}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1684}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking back, maybe I needed to go through that disappointment to take me where I was in 2021 - more of a confident swimmer.\\\"\", \"from\": 1693, \"to\": 1819, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that disappointment\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1756}, {\"ngram\": \"a confident swimmer\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1817}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Smithstands to become only the second swimmer in history after Penny Heyns in 1996 to complete the 100m and 200m breaststroke golden double at the same Olympics event.\", \"from\": 1821, \"to\": 1988, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1884, \"end\": 1895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penelope_Heyns\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Penny Heyns\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Penelope_Heyns\", \"dbpedia\": \"ht